main: ^Hello traveler! Are you here to listen to my music? To experience the Tlakahanian culture:
^Hi. It's good to see that you are happy now. I have a story for you.
cleanerToArtist: ^(You tell the artist how you changed his past.)
^Oh really?! This is unbelievable! Even if it's not true. It's a beautifull story. I will gladly give you this. Please take this.
